        He has professional experience in HTML/CSS/JS, React, Webpack, jQuery,
        Playwright, and SQL (SQLite).
      </p>
      <p>
        Matt has also worked with Java, Spring, Astro, Next.js, PostgreSQL,
        Drizzle, Cloudflare Workers/Pages, Inngest, Vercel's deployment
        platform, GitHub Actions, Docker/Docker Compose, AWS EC2, and Google
        Cloud Run.
      </p>

      <p>
        In short, Matt keeps up with the cutting edge of the web development
        world without neglecting his fundamentals. He's confident he can hit the
        ground running in React codebases — he's done it before!
      </p>
